text:
I see... you're really pulling off this look, huh.
It's really highlighting your features... As expected...

The way you enjoy it varies depending on how you wear it.
With that said... here, take this.

When I stopped by a shop earlier,
I thought it'd suit you, so I went ahead and bought it.

It's a bit different from your usual style
but I thought it'd look good.

Different from usual... I see...
Yeah... I should give something different a try...!

Thanks, Mamimi!
Let me hold it up to see how it would look────

H-How is it...?
Does it suit me?
